race.comment: COOL PANELS (3) returned in fine fashion with a solid Kilcoy win before being right there in the two subsequent outings since. Has placed two from two around this circuit and goes well for hoop Cartwright. Should be right there when the judge calls a halt. BUSKER (2) strips fitter second-up from the break and is drawn to get a gun run from the inside alley. Certainly in the mix if he brings his A-game. BRUTAL GLORY (10) draws favourably and will be ready to peak now fourth run in. Top-three candidate. EVERYWHERE (8) saves his best form for this distance range and is worth including in multiples.
